"{\"uid\": \"dailypost.ng-2024-02-20-2024-olympic-qualifiers-waldrum-reveals-new-mission-with-super-falcons\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Published  on  By  Super Falcons head coach, Randy Waldrum says he is determined to help the Super Falcons secure a place at the 2024 Olympic Games in Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 157, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19, \"end\": 32, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Super Falcons\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 45, \"end\": 58, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Waldrum\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Randy Waldrum\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Waldrum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Waldrum\"}, {\"begin\": 93, \"end\": 106, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Super Falcons\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 151, \"end\": 156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999997496372857, \"rank\": 2.50362887429641e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The nine-time African champions have failed to qualify for the last three editions of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 159, \"to\": 258, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Waldrum's charges will continue their quest for a place in Paris 2024 when they take on fierce rivals, Indomitable Lionesses of Cameroon in the third round of the qualifiers.\", \"from\": 260, \"to\": 434, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 319, \"end\": 329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.4778321511488854e-14, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The first leg will take place at the Stade de la Reunification, Douala on Friday.\", \"from\": 436, \"to\": 517, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The reverse fixture is slated for the Moshood Abiola Stadium, Abuja next week Monday.\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 604, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 557, \"end\": 571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moshood_Abiola\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Moshood Abiola\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moshood_Abiola\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moshood_Abiola\"}, {\"begin\": 581, \"end\": 586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abuja\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3801771485993015e-20, \"text\": \"Abuja\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abuja\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abuja\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The American, who recently penned a new contract with the Nigeria Football Federation, NFF, stated that it is important for his side to qualify for the Olympics after their long absence.\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 792, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 610, \"end\": 618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9988758275792688, \"rank\": 0.0011117754290875302, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 664, \"end\": 691, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Football_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nigeria Football Federation\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Football_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Football_Federation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The goal obviously is to qualify for the Olympics.\", \"from\": 794, \"to\": 845, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We can not look ahead of ourselves and say this is what we want to achieve at the Olympics, \\\"Waldrum told the Super Falcons media team.\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 981, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 956, \"end\": 969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Super Falcons\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Qualification is going to be the primary goal.\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 1030, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Everyone knows we have a difficult set of matches coming up against Cameroon.\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1108, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1099, \"end\": 1107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameroon_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9996222096785512, \"rank\": 0.0003779330569822798, \"text\": \"Cameroon\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameroon_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameroon_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The focus is now on the two matches.\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1147, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cameroon stopped us from going to the Olympics a few years back, I think in 2012.\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1229, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1148, \"end\": 1156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameroon_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9996222096785512, \"rank\": 0.0003779330569822798, \"text\": \"Cameroon\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameroon_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameroon_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The two countries know each other very well.\", \"from\": 1230, \"to\": 1274, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They have lots of talents and are very dangerous, especially their counter-attacking style of play.\", \"from\": 1276, \"to\": 1376, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I really like our squad, I like the team chemistry.\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1434, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are able to get all our players back in for these matches which are very important.\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1521, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So, if we can put together the performances like we did at the last World Cup, then I fancy our chances.\", \"from\": 1523, \"to\": 1628, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We just need to build on what we did at the World Cup and even do better.\", \"from\": 1630, \"to\": 1704, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The difficult part in all these matches is that the window of time in the international break does not allow for a lot of training time.\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1841, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We will have to use our experience at the World Cup to win these games because we have few days to train.\\\"\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1950, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"NFF announces date for 2024 Federation Cup  AFCON 2025: Preliminary round draw out [Full Fixtures]  2026 WAFCON: 'It would not happen for other tournaments' - Super Falcons' Plumptre slams CAF  WAFCON 2026: Super Falcons Ajibade disappointed with postponement  WAFCON 2026: Super Falcons decamped after postponement  Friendly: Cameroon coach gives reason for defeat to Super Falcons  Friendly: Babajide relishes Super Falcons' win over Cameroon  Friendly: Super Falcons floor Cameroon 3-1 in Yaounde  Copyright \\u00a9Daily Post Media Ltd\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 2484, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2141, \"end\": 2144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Confederation_of_African_Football\", \"score\": 0.999999929596245, \"rank\": 7.040381475582963e-08, \"text\": \"CAF\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Confederation_of_African_Football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Confederation_of_African_Football\"}, {\"begin\": 2159, \"end\": 2172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Super Falcons\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2226, \"end\": 2239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Super Falcons\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2279, \"end\": 2287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameroon_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9996222096785512, \"rank\": 0.0003779330569822798, \"text\": \"Cameroon\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameroon_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameroon_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2321, \"end\": 2334, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", 